{"tid":1000541,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【華為危機】拒絕美要求對付中俄 匈牙利總理：想保持中立","createTime":"2019-01-29T13:08:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T15:13:37.000Z","uid":70063,"like":3,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ca3bf17af84fb3879211d9fb5fb37ccb3035f824","tid":1000541,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T13:08:58.000Z","msg":"美國《華爾街日報》於當地時間28日報道，針對美國敦促其盟國對俄羅斯和中國採取更強硬立場，匈牙利總理奧爾班（Viktor Orb&aacute;n）近日向美國外交官表明，他希望自己的國家「像奧地利一樣保持中立」。評論認為，這一表態加劇了匈牙利正脫離美國影響力範圍的擔憂。據報，美國國務卿蓬佩奧計劃下月出訪匈牙利。<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，歐爾班上月在布達佩斯會見美國駐匈牙利大使時表達該國立場，對於美國為遏制莫斯科和北京政府在歐洲影響力的施壓行為，歐爾班表示強烈反對。匈牙利高級官員表示，該國將繼續履行對北約的承諾，但不準備加入美國與俄羅斯和中國針鋒相對的陣營。該官員說：「有人教育我們甚麼才是對待中國的正確態度，說我們是『中國的代理人』，我們反對這樣。」<br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》報道，歐爾班認為，是否允許中國和俄羅斯企業在該國電訊、能源和銀行等領域作出投資，這些都是匈牙利的主權，捷克總統澤曼也曾發表類似言論。美國政府一名官員說：「在中歐，不僅是匈牙利，採取更中立立場的捷克和斯洛伐克也受政治因素影響。」他表示擔憂：「中國人正利用基礎設施項目和電訊交易，在其中的多個國家進行滲透，行動力度很大。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190129/59199794\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190129%2F59199794&d=2pBoyAcJJfm%2FTk9I6oZxMMemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=a709e991\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190129%2F59199794&h=fcbe645d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190129/59199794</a>"},{"pid":"9c20b9c0f26eb293f3ae063b8242dc33255dc573","tid":1000541,"uid":1712,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T13:13:00.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n華為大大個hub喺度<br />\n緊係唔幫手對付啦"},{"pid":"a75ec505d3f25faefbff4e2edcb221dc34e9ee98","tid":1000541,"uid":53705,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T13:13:22.000Z","msg":"美國:「你中唔中立都對我無影響嫁啦」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b3db8ce9ba7044a3fecf28ce4a0d058e9dae0c","tid":1000541,"uid":196671,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T13:21:52.000Z","msg":"三場世界大戰都企錯邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e9e572a9ad9a464dc9958335c7845bb7fa9544d","tid":1000541,"uid":38904,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"14b3db8ce9ba7044a3fecf28ce4a0d058e9dae0c","tid":1000541,"uid":196671,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T13:21:52.000Z","msg":"三場世界大戰都企錯邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T13:37:05.000Z","msg":"德國就醒目啦今次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1d6f3fcb41cf14bf561d6017ba176707d27c863","tid":1000541,"uid":39550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T13:59:08.000Z","msg":"低能仔"},{"pid":"e68150327fb84cf9a43f0cd5ee1baedd93a772f0","tid":1000541,"uid":157369,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T14:01:54.000Z","msg":"奧匈 捷斯<br />\n真係衰咁多次都要跟錯大佬<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"136bf9f1e8f2efc7a14273f0813bc467275aa5e2","tid":1000541,"uid":171866,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T14:06:37.000Z","msg":"班西人實無睇過德國人，印度人，支那人修天國電梯個故仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4af9f342d6b2b7042d0ff6f39d9e40139ba3a2fa","tid":1000541,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T14:14:13.000Z","msg":"on仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"563c0e5934f670a4222a502bb364ca7abae5ee36","tid":1000541,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T14:16:06.000Z","msg":"佢之前ot個奴隸法都搞到日日反政府示威, 自己都理唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bac4a88e4b1ed9e8a3749fd8e07497832ea8e22d","tid":1000541,"uid":25688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"136bf9f1e8f2efc7a14273f0813bc467275aa5e2","tid":1000541,"uid":171866,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T14:06:37.000Z","msg":"班西人實無睇過德國人，印度人，支那人修天國電梯個故仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T14:20:30.000Z","msg":"講黎聽下"},{"pid":"9c494ff62f4fd1b1f8cc69014a2b466e292e0637","tid":1000541,"uid":171866,"like":2,"dislike":18,"score":-16,"quote":{"pid":"bac4a88e4b1ed9e8a3749fd8e07497832ea8e22d","tid":1000541,"uid":25688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"136bf9f1e8f2efc7a14273f0813bc467275aa5e2","tid":1000541,"uid":171866,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T14:06:37.000Z","msg":"班西人實無睇過德國人，印度人，支那人修天國電梯個故仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T14:20:30.000Z","msg":"講黎聽下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T14:27:15.000Z","msg":"天堂的门坏了，上帝要招标重修。<br />\n<br />\n印度人说：3000弄好，理由是材料费1000，人工费1000，我自己赚1000。<br />\n<br />\n德国人说：要6000，材料费2000，人工2000，自己赚2000。<br />\n<br />\n中国人淡定地说：这个要9000，3000给你，3000我的，剩下3000给那个印度人干。<br />\n<br />\n上帝拍案：中国人中标！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n后来地狱的门也坏了，阎王吸取了上帝的教训，制定控制价3000。<br />\n<br />\n德国人看了一眼，走了。<br />\n<br />\n印度人报价3000。<br />\n<br />\n中国人给了评标的小鬼500，报价3000，又中标了。<br />\n<br />\n德国人、印度人很纳闷。之后，中国人花了500材料，500人工，修了一半宣布停工。拖了半年，阎王被逼追加投资3000，完工。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再后来天堂连接地狱的电梯坏了，也要重修。经过前面两次教训后，控制定价3000而且规定要一次性修好。<br />\n<br />\n德国人又来，看了一下走了。<br />\n<br />\n印度人报价3000。<br />\n<br />\n中国人也报价3000，并称完工后有茅台送，又中标了。<br />\n<br />\n拿到钱后中国人开工。材料500，人工500。完工后，上帝叫人验收。事先收了中国人红包500的验收员声称&ldquo;合格&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n不久又坏了，安监、质检（都收了钱）等部门说超载所致，要重建。上帝被逼追加资金9000重建！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再再后来，通往人间的大门也坏了，死的上不来，投胎的下不去，上帝与阎王都着急。问题很严重。<br />\n<br />\n经过前几次的教训之后，天国严格定价3000，监理、审计现场跟踪！并且免费保修1亿年。<br />\n<br />\n德国人被吓跑了。<br />\n<br />\n印度人报价3000。<br />\n<br />\n中国人来了，报无偿修理，且免费保修2亿年，但要1亿年的管理权，上帝和阎王都同意了。<br />\n<br />\n中国人修好了门后，在门口设了个收费站，死了要上天堂的收500，下去投胎每人每次500，双向收费且上不封顶，给500的投到欧洲，给1000的投胎到美国，逃费的一律投到中国。<br />\n<br />\n经过4次招标后，印度人和德国人~<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上帝和阎王崩溃！"},{"pid":"e5964123187aeeae7574ce48c9a360369c51a2bd","tid":1000541,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14b3db8ce9ba7044a3fecf28ce4a0d058e9dae0c","tid":1000541,"uid":196671,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T13:21:52.000Z","msg":"三場世界大戰都企錯邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T14:38:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a870a963e070958ce7b1bca199d808295019fffd","tid":1000541,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5964123187aeeae7574ce48c9a360369c51a2bd","tid":1000541,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14b3db8ce9ba7044a3fecf28ce4a0d058e9dae0c","tid":1000541,"uid":196671,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T13:21:52.000Z","msg":"三場世界大戰都企錯邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T14:38:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T14:39:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"381ce3a14b079f860c4fb752d19b2bab3d8c4e1d","tid":1000541,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c494ff62f4fd1b1f8cc69014a2b466e292e0637",